  "title": "Project Engineer (1 year contract/ West)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Basic Salary:</strong> $3,000 – $4,000<br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Mon–Fri, 8:00am – 5:10pm<br /><strong>Location:</strong> Pioneer (company transport provided at multiple pick-up points)<br /><strong>Benefits:</strong> Variable Bonus, 14 AL, Medical Coverage<br /><strong>Employment Type:</strong> 1-year contract (renewable)</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Plan and execute engineering projects within scope, budget, and timeline.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with internal teams, vendors, and clients to ensure smooth delivery.</p></li><li><p>Review technical drawings and ensure compliance with standards and specifications.</p></li><li><p>Track progress, prepare reports, and resolve technical issues.</p></li><li><p>Source and procure required equipment/materials.</p></li><li><p>Perform site monitoring and coordination.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma/Degree in Mechanical, Electrical, or related engineering field.</p></li><li><p>1–2 years of project engineering experience preferred; fresh graduates welcome.</p></li><li><p>Strong project management and problem-solving skills.</p></li><li><p>Proficient in Microsoft Project and/or related project management tools.</p></li></ul><p>☎ Call 6817-2691<br />✉ WhatsApp 9422-1220<br />EA License No: 15C7752<br />EA Personnel No: R22111807<br />EA Personnel Name: Yap Teng hui</p>",
